# tcpq - TCP Packet Analyzer

A Qt-based network packet analyzer inspired by tcpdump.

## Features

- Packet capture using libpcap
- Real-time packet display
- TCP/UDP/ICMP protocol analysis
- Filter expression support
- Qt GUI with packet list and detail views

## Requirements

- Qt5
- libpcap-dev

## Building

```bash
qmake -o Makefile tcpq.pro
make
```

## Usage

```bash
./tcpq                    # Capture on default interface
./tcpq -i eth0           # Capture on eth0
./tcpq -f "tcp port 80"  # Apply filter
```

## Architecture

- `src/main.cpp` - Application entry point
- `src/packetcapture.cpp` - Packet capture engine
- `src/packetanalyzer.cpp` - Protocol analysis
- `ui/mainwindow.ui` - Main window UI
- `include/` - Header files

